SUB_W09_EVAR_AMYA_OPENING_120_CUT_000_05.text:
Oh, I'm nothing so special;
merely a prisoner of the royals
and nothing more.

SUB_W09_EVAR_AMYA_LAST_200_CUT_000_010.text:
Spare me your counsel and step aside;
I've brought a cracking offering that
is certain to please His Majesty.

SUB_W09_EVAR_AMYA_UNDERCITY_010_CUT_000_.text:
Is this stuff here what you guys use
for money? 'Cause I don't need it,
so help yourself if you want.
